{"tid":2227851,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"穩一隻PS1既舊日文game","createTime":"2020-10-03T06:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T08:17:03.000Z","uid":219590,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91f8efd1707305cb398c41fb201ca4cacf45a101","tid":2227851,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2B8sTS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2B8sTS.jpg&h=e7e35c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲畫面分成四格，然後你係自己嗰一格度可以起嘢，每一個格仔都有d專屬怪獸。一開始每個人d怪獸都係好廢，細細隻但好多，之後可以變到大大隻。適當時候可以去打人。<br />\n<br />\nPS1日文game黎，唔知有無人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前細細個有玩，但記憶好模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6fe35a26370e0ab4dc646898209e9d8a48e28f","tid":2227851,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"補充番：畫面風格係似日系動漫feel"},{"pid":"2cad12277ec44c6e75c81f05a6bfd758cca1f903","tid":2227851,"uid":160263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"club penguin"},{"pid":"a57eae1b0612f74b18e17aa5a4c7d8e7f23d9297","tid":2227851,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2cad12277ec44c6e75c81f05a6bfd758cca1f903","tid":2227851,"uid":160263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"club penguin"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:10:25.000Z","msg":"PS1, 日式動漫畫風"},{"pid":"f07a0ae7223e37481c39ceba90bf5ddcffa699be","tid":2227851,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1b27c4e1d8402f81db3da28cd84f42df9d1b9ec3","tid":2227851,"uid":255868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"lm 有印象同朋友4個人玩過 唔記得咩名 <br />\n我都想搵返隻驚名"},{"pid":"78b44367066c1c735599eeae0e5a2ca8f7a415e2","tid":2227851,"uid":219590,"like":0,"dis